Age < 18 > =35 year ; PCOS ; Endometriosis ; Subjects evidence autoimmune rheumatic disease ; Hypersensitivity active substance excipients ( lactose ) ; Abnormal bleeding undetermined origin ; Subject find positive antiTSH antibody ( i.e . suffer thyroidal disease ) ; Uncontrolled adrenal dysfunction ; Neoplasia ; Severe impairment renal and/or hepatic function ; Use concomitant medication might interfere study evaluation ( e.g . immunosuppressant , nonstudy hormonal medication , therapeutic protein like insulin , growth hormone… ) .
